On my way to see The Social Network. Let's see if the expectations can be upheld.
All of my family is too lazy to host thanksgiving dinner so no turkey for me.
Almost time to go home and test out the new speakers. Class is just too slow.
Really needs to acquire planet earth in HD. Morgan Freemans voice + awesome animals is total win.
Went to A&W, got 2 mozza burgers and chubby chicken burger yet am not disgustingly full.
Was at the casino and will most likely be going back. Let's hope I can be lucky for once.
